ion-attachment-515933\"><a href=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-515933 size-full\" src=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-300x199.jpg 300w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-1024x679.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-768x509.jpg 768w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-150x100.jpg 150w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-600x398.jpg 600w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-696x462.jpg 696w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-1068x708.jpg 1068w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-4-633x420.jpg 633w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"796\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-515933\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thủ phủ của bang Ticino đặt tại thành phố Bellinzona. Ảnh: Đinh Thanh Vân</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_515935\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-515935\"><a href=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-515935 size-full\" src=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-300x200.jpg 300w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-150x100.jpg 150w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-600x400.jpg 600w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-696x463.jpg 696w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-1068x711.jpg 1068w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-7-631x420.jpg 631w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-515935\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ngôn ngữ chính tại Ticino là tiếng Ý, tuy nhiên, du khách vẫn có thể sử dụng tiếng Anh để giao tiếp. Ảnh: Đinh Thanh Vân</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_515936\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-515936\"><a href=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-515936\" src=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-300x200.jpg 300w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-150x100.jpg 150w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-600x400.jpg 600w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-696x463.jpg 696w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-1068x711.jpg 1068w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-12-631x420.jpg 631w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-515936\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Du khách check-in tại “khung hình Grand Tour” – nơi đánh dấu các địa điểm nổi bật ở Thụy Sĩ. Ảnh: Đinh Thanh Vân</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_515938\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-515938\"><a href=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-515938 size-full\" src=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-300x200.jpg 300w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-150x100.jpg 150w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-600x399.jpg 600w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-696x463.jpg 696w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-1068x710.jpg 1068w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-19-632x420.jpg 632w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"798\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-515938\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Theo trang thông tin bang Ticino, mùa Hè có thời tiết thích hợp tham gia các hoạt động như đi dạo, chèo thuyền kayak trên hồ Lugano hay trekking khám phá thung lũng Blenio… Ảnh: Đinh Thanh Vân</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_515939\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-515939\"><a href=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-515939 size-full\" src=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-300x200.jpg 300w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-150x100.jpg 150w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-600x400.jpg 600w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-696x463.jpg 696w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-1068x711.jpg 1068w, https://cdn.sgtiepthi.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ticino-16-631x420.jpg 631w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-515939\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cầu Ponte Diga di Melide nhìn từ xe lửa đi lên đỉnh núi Monte San Salvatore. Ảnh: Đinh Thanh Vân</figcaption></figure>', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-09-20 09:10:14', '2024-09-20 09:10:14', '', 10, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=12', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
